24
00:02:11,279 --> 00:02:13,900
Maharani memang sudah tahu
hubungan Tan'er dan Mutiara Zhenhun.

25
00:02:14,079 --> 00:02:17,320
Jadi, dia pasti dibawa
ke Altar Lingyou.

26
00:02:30,839 --> 00:02:32,639
Tan'er.

27
00:02:42,839 --> 00:02:43,860
