111
00:09:27,020 --> 00:09:28,120
Dia ingin manfaatkan Tan'er…

112
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:30,700
…untuk bangunkan Maharani dengan
energi sihir Mutiara Zhenhun.

113
00:09:31,359 --> 00:09:34,860
