nyawa Maharani,…

126
00:10:04,970 --> 00:10:06,660
…juga tak akan melukai
Tuan Putri ke-2.

127
00:10:06,970 --> 00:10:09,500
Sebaliknya Mo Liancheng,
kau berniat memberontak.

128
00:10:10,020 --> 00:10:12,210
Mohon Jenderal menangkapnya.

129
00:10:12,210 --> 00:10:13,460
Kuperingatkan kau sekali lagi.

130
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:16,400
Mutiara Zhenhun mudah hilang
kendali jika digunakan begini.

131
00:10:16,530 --> 00:10:19,260
Maharani dan Tan'er
bisa mengalami bahaya.

132
00:10:19,650 --> 00:10:23,180
Di seluruh istana, hanya sedikit
orang yang tahu Mutiara Zhenhun.

133
00:10:23,650 --> 00:10:25,750
Namun, kau bisa menjelaskannya
dengan begitu tepat.

134
00:10:25,890 --> 00:10:29,140
Kau pasti sudah lama buat rencana
dan ingin mencelakakan Maharani!

135
00:10:29,290 --> 00:10:30,060
Tuan Xiao.

136
00:10:30,140 --> 00:10:31,620
Kusarankan kau segera berhenti.

137
00:10:31,820 --> 00:10:33,580
Jika Jenderal juga ikut dibutakan,…

138
00:10:33,970 --> 00:10:36,500
…maka jangan salahkan aku
mengabaikan hubungan kita.

139
00:10:36,700 --> 00:10:37,820
Tangkap Mo Liancheng!

140
00:10:38,700 --> 00:10:39,720
Cheng Cheng, hati-hati!

141
